{
  "title": "ISic003161. Fragment of an epitaph",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa, Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag, 2014-09</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <span data-text=\"καλανδῶν\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"kalendae\">καλανδῶν</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἰου\n                    λίου\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Iulius\">Ἰου-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[λίου?</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐτελεύτα\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">ἐ]τελεύτα</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φηλη\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φηλη\"><span data-text=\"Φηλη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Φηλη\">Φηλη</span></span></span>-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"34\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἐτ]ῶν</span>  <span data-text=\"κε\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"κε\"><span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">κ͡ε</span></span>´ <span data-text=\"ἐνθά\n                    δε\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ἐνθά-<br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[δε]</span>  <span data-text=\"καθίζεται\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"καθίζω\">[καθ]ίζ[εται</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\"> [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <span data-text=\"καλανδῶν\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"kalendae\">καλανδῶν</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἰουλίου\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Iulius\">Ἰουλίου</span> [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <span data-text=\"ἐτελεύτα\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">ἐτελεύτα</span>  <span data-text=\"Φηλη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Φηλη\">Φηλη</span> [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] <span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"34\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἐτῶν</span>  <span data-text=\"κε\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"κε\">κε</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ἐνθάδε</span>  <span data-text=\"καθίζεται\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"καθίζω\">καθίζεται</span> [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa, Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag, 2014-09</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"καλανδῶν\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"kalendae\">ΚΑΛΑΝΔΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"Ἰου\n                    λίου\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Iulius\">ΙΟΥ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>[....</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span><span data-text=\"ἐτελεύτα\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">.]ΤΕΛΕΥΤΑ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φηλη\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φηλη\"><span data-text=\"Φηλη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Φηλη\">ΦΗΛΗ</span></span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span><span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"34\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">..]ΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"κε\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"κε\"><span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Κ͡Ε</span></span><span data-text=\"ἐνθά\n                    δε\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[..</span><span data-text=\"καθίζεται\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"καθίζω\">...]ΙΖ[....</span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"καλανδῶν\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"kalendae\">ΚΑΛΑΝΔΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"Ἰουλίου\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Iulius\">ΙΟΥΛΙΟΥ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"ἐτελεύτα\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"τελευτάω\">ΕΤΕΛΕΥΤΑ</span><span data-text=\"Φηλη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Φηλη\">ΦΗΛΗ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"ἐτῶν\" data-n=\"34\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"κε\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"κε\">ΚΕ</span><span data-text=\"ἐνθάδε\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ἐνθάδε\">ΕΝΘΑΔΕ</span><span data-text=\"καθίζεται\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"καθίζω\">ΚΑΘΙΖΕΤΑΙ</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003161.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2014-09-09\" src=\"ISic003161-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003161.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2014-09-09\" src=\"ISic003161-thumb.jpg\"></a><a href=\"ISic003161_rear.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2014-09-09\" src=\"ISic003161_rear-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003161_rear.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2014-09-09\" src=\"ISic003161_rear-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text from autopsy</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"2-3\">2-3: <span>Gentili: Φηλη-|[κί]ων κὲ; the reading adopted here suggested by Tod in SEG</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>[---] the kalends of July(?), Phele[?] passed away aged 25 years. Here they lie [-?-].</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The presence of a supraline above the letters ΚΕ in line 3 very strongly suggests a numeral, and not κε for και, since κε is not an abbreviation, which would be the only other purpose of the supraline. The resolution of the name Φηλη- is uncertain.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 16.0536 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Gentili NSA 1956 116, fig.10 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Lunate letters, somewhat irregular in height / layout, deeply carved.</p> Line 1-4  10-20  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
